<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">limited</ENAMEX>. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">office</ENAMEX> saved <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$6,600</NUMEX> over <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">about 33 months</TIMEX>. This office
