<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">contractor</ENAMEX>. However, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Department</ENAMEX> rejected the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">contractor</ENAMEX>'s
