<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">contractor</ENAMEX>'s proposal, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Interior</ENAMEX> would have had to provide the
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">contractor</ENAMEX> with data on the frequent flyer miles received by its
